title: Icon Bridal are taking part in Strictly Northampton! (Northamptonshire Chamber)
text: ( Source : Northamptonshire Chamber ) Amy Watts and Tracey Hales , owners of Kettering based Icon Bridal are taking part in Strictly Northampton , an event in its sixth year, which is in aid of local Charity , Cynthia Spencer . Amy is a contestant
